text: btw those blue unis last night were :ok_hand:

So, funny story about those blue uni’s. Apparently they’ve always had the blue on blue combo, and that was how Nike originally designed them way back in the day. All the dudes on the team really liked the blue on blue, but Elway hated it. He thought it was too flashy, so he veto’d them for the Blue + White pants, which stuck for the next decade or so.
i prefer the blue on white, but that’s just me. maybe cause it’s the first thing i think of when i used to watch the broncos as a kid
also, they won a SB in those, so i’m with you. White on White are the GOAT.
